OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and occasional
OL,6,Fshowers, some wintry over Shetland
OL,7,Fthis morning. The showers fading in
OL,8,Fafternoon with the westerly winds
OL,9,Feasing, then cloud and rain will reach
OL,10,FOrkney by evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain over Orkney turning
OL,13,Fheavy and extending to Shetland with
OL,14,Fsnow on hills, Strengthening winds
OL,15,Fwith gales or severe gales for a time
OL,16,Ftonight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
