OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAny remaining heavy rain, hill
OL,6,Fsnow and severe gales over Shetland
OL,7,Fclearing in morning leaving a bright
OL,8,Fday with sunny intervals and a few
OL,9,Fshowers.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry and bright on Monday and Tuesday
OL,13,Fwith some sunny spells. Cloudier on
OL,14,FWednesday with chance of rain or
OL,15,Fshowers.
